ActExport Development Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of KAREN MACWILLIAM of Wolfville, Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Export Development Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Jacques Boivin, whose term has expired.
